# Workflow Protocol

## Session start

- Check `docs/decisions/` if the task touches business logic or prior decisions.
- If requirements are unclear, use `grill-me` before proposing anything.

## Vertical slices

Work in minimal end-to-end slices (DB + logic + UI). Verify each slice before starting the next.

## Skills

| Task | Claude Code | Cursor |
|---|---|---|
| Alignment before feature | `grill-me` | `grill-me` |
| Break into slices | `slice` | `slice` |
| Business logic / backend | `backend` | `backend-server-actions` |
| TDD | `superpowers:test-driven-development` | `testing-quality-gates` |
| Debugging | `superpowers:systematic-debugging` | — |
| Final verification | `done` | `done` |
